  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00565', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-112-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關團體中領導者自我揭露（disclosure）的敘述 ，下列何者錯誤？', '["目的是讓領導者完整表達個人想法與經驗", "希望能在團體中引發深度溝通", "讓成員知道領導者了解他們的處境", "希望創造一種示範作用，讓成員比較放心談論"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "13927e4759e3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9f92f5035bc4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "502", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00566', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-112-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '在個案工作中有多種技巧，下列敘述何者正確？', '["「同是天涯淪落人，相逢何必曾相識」這句話適用於同理更勝於同情", "傾聽是同理溝通的開始，而同理的回應是有層次的", "會談中多使用「你」為開頭，可以有效讓服務對象感受到社會工作者的真誠", "每一次當服務對象想了解社會工作者的經驗時，社會工作者應果斷拒絕並讓其知道專業關係中不適宜 分享個人經驗"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "13927e4759e3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9f92f5035bc4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "502", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00567', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-112-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '團體的類型有多種區分方法，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["成長性團體屬於任務性團體（task-centeredgroups）的一種", "處遇性團體著重在處理成員的社會心理議題", "任務性團體的任務一旦完成團體就結束", "無刻意干涉所形成的團體是自然團體（naturalgroup），被要求而組成的團體是組成團體（formedgroup）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "13927e4759e3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9f92f5035bc4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "502", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00568', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-112-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '在個案工作會談過程，服務對象言談不清楚或語意模糊，社會工作者不太了解服務對象想要表達的意思， 可以簡述服務對象的話，並確認所傳達訊息的真正意思，這個會談的技巧稱為：', '["溫暖", "催化", "澄清", "面質"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "13927e4759e3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9f92f5035bc4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "502", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00569', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-112-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '將假釋出獄者置於假釋官之下加以監督輔導，防止其再犯，並促進其適應社會生活的作法。這是屬於下 列何種社區處遇方式？', '["保護管束", "監外就業", "更生保護", "中途之家"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "13927e4759e3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9f92f5035bc4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "502", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00570', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-112-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '依行政院於2005年訂定的「建立社區關懷據點實施計畫」由在地人提供在地服務，建立社區自主運作模 式。下列何者不是「社區照顧關懷據點」提供的服務項目？', '["關懷訪視和電話問安、諮詢及轉介服務", "餐飲服務", "健康促進", "交通服務"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "13927e4759e3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9f92f5035bc4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "502", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 35, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00571', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-112-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '社會工作者在災害的緊急救援階段時期，提供心理支持，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["緊急收容中心主任應安排社會工作師、心理師、諮商師、精神科醫師等前來為災民進行災後創傷壓力 之處理", "心理支持等有空再做", "若災民需要收驚、拜拜、祈禱等，專業人員不宜排斥", "評估那些災民需要陪伴，組織志工陪伴"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "13927e4759e3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9f92f5035bc4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "502", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00572', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-112-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '自1990年後，英國的醫療保健服務提出了中間服務的概念，下列敘述何者正確？', '["限於提供中期復健", "通常在急重症醫院內發展", "服務目標達成的時間壓力非常急迫", "相當需要社會工作者的參與介入"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "13927e4759e3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9f92f5035bc4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "502", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00573', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-112-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '身心障礙福利機構在社區內辦理住宿服務，常遇抗爭，下列敘述何者符合「身心障礙者權益保障法」之 規定？', '["身心障礙福利機構應努力建立社區關係，如未果必須遷移他處", "給予社區居民補償", "地方政府應協助排除障礙", "身心障礙福利機構得直接進駐，無視居民反對"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "13927e4759e3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9f92f5035bc4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "502", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00574', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-112-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '政府機關（構）及公營事業機構自行或委託辦理諮詢性電話服務工作，電話值機人數在10人以上者，應 進用視障者達電話值機人數的比例，下列何者正確？', '["1/10以上", "1/15以上", "1/20以上", "1/25以上"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "13927e4759e3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9f92f5035bc4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "502", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL)
